[size=12pt][b]4. Network & Stability Improvements[/b][/size]

[b]v0.0.9-beta - Peer Discovery Fix:[/b]
• ✅ Fixed libp2p event loop termination on dial errors
• ✅ Real-time peer counting with thread-safe atomic counters
• ✅ Enhanced logging for connection debugging
• ✅ Multi-layer peer discovery: mDNS + Kademlia DHT + Bootstrap nodes

[b]v0.0.8-beta - Cross-Node Synchronization:[/b]
• ✅ Reliable blockchain state synchronization across nodes
• ✅ Improved consensus finality
• ✅ Better handling of network partitions

[b]Critical Bug Fixes:[/b]
• ✅ [b]Balance Persistence Bug[/b] - Mining rewards no longer lost on service restart
• ✅ [b]Mixer Address Parsing[/b] - Fixed "qnk" prefix causing funds to go to wrong address
• ✅ [b]SSE Event Delivery[/b] - Increased buffer 10x to prevent dropped balance updates

