[size=14pt][b]💬 Why Q-NarwhalKnight?[/b][/size]

[b]1. Quantum-Resistant Future-Proofing[/b]
While other blockchains scramble to add post-quantum cryptography after quantum computers arrive, Q-NarwhalKnight is [b]quantum-ready from day one[/b].

[b]2. Real Privacy, Not Theater[/b]
Many "privacy coins" use weak anonymity techniques that leak metadata. Q-NarwhalKnight uses [b]ZK-STARK proofs[/b] - provably zero-knowledge cryptography that hides everything.

[b]3. Enterprise-Grade Infrastructure[/b]
Privacy-as-a-Service brings enterprise reliability to privacy: SLA guarantees, dedicated support, compliance tools, and production SDKs.

[b]4. Cross-Chain Compatibility[/b]
Instead of forcing users to switch to a new blockchain, PaaS brings privacy to [b]existing blockchains[/b] like Bitcoin and Ethereum.

[b]5. Open Source & Transparent[/b]
All code is Apache 2.0 licensed. Security through cryptography, not obscurity.

